<p>CodeX Accelerator serves this purpose for Use Cases around cancer (mCODE standard), cardiovascular disease, and genomics, so far. Other governance schemes are possible but would require more effort to startup and engage across specialties.</p>

      <p><%= image_tag 'governance_structure.png', :width => '100%', :class => 'py-5' %></p>
  
      <h3 id="growth">Grow the community</h3>
      <p>Each Use Case has the potential to attract new participants.</p>
      <p>Ideally, engage multiple representatives for each role to expand input and build redundancy.</p>
  
